OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly but sunny start to the
OL,6,Fday with plenty of sunshine, though
OL,7,Fthe odd light shower may be possible
OL,8,Fat first. Pleasant in the sunny spells
OL,9,Fthis afternoon, with temperatures
OL,10,Faround the seasonal average.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying dry across the region
OL,13,Ftonight. Turning chilly under the
OL,14,Fclear skies with a few mist and fog
OL,15,Fpatches possible.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FAny mist or fog will quickly
OL,18,Fclear in the morning. Staying dry with
OL,19,Fsunny spells at first, but cloud
OL,20,Flikely increasing during the afternoon
OL,21,Fin the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
