OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FLargely cloudy during early next week
OL,7,Fwith showers possible at times. Some
OL,8,Fbrighter interlude are also possible,
OL,9,Fparticularly in the west. Windy at
OL,10,Ftimes, especially over the Moors.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
